01:43:45,803 --> 01:43:47,220
Of course you can't.

1023
01:43:47,388 --> 01:43:51,015
Although you don't know it...
you love me.

1024
01:43:51,600 --> 01:43:55,311
Because you know that without me,
you are nothing.

1025
01:43:55,479 --> 01:43:57,981
And I am only a shadow without you.

1026
01:45:13,349 --> 01:45:15,892
Julia, why did you lock the door?

1027
01:45:20,064 --> 01:45:21,981
- Hello?
- Inspector. It's Julia.

1028
01:45:22,191 --> 01:45:23,232
Julia, it's you.

1029
01:45:23,400 --> 01:45:27,111
Listen to me, because this is
the last time I'll call you.

1030
01:45:27,279 --> 01:45:30,948
- Calm down.
- He's locked me in my house.

1031
01:45:31,116 --> 01:45:33,284
- Calm down, Julia.
- He's going to kill me.

1032
01:45:33,452 --> 01:45:37,872
If you don't come, it will be too late.
You have to believe me. Please.

1033
01:45:37,998 --> 01:45:40,458
- Julia, please, calm down.
- Are you listening to me?

1034
01:45:42,586 --> 01:45:44,045
Inspector?

1035
01:45:50,969 --> 01:45:52,345
Julia!

1036
01:47:57,429 --> 01:48:00,431
Julia, police!
Cover the stairs and the hallway.

1037
01:48:00,599 --> 01:48:02,433
Julia, are you there?

1038
01:48:02,601 --> 01:48:05,436
It's Dimas. Can you hear me?

1039
01:48:06,104 --> 01:48:08,147
- Julia, what are you doing?
- Shut up!

1040
01:48:08,357 --> 01:48:11,275
- What's going on?
- I said shut up!

1041
01:48:22,287 --> 01:48:24,789
Can you see him?
Can you see him, Inspector?

1042
01:48:24,957 --> 01:48:28,626
Police! Put the knife down!
Put your hands above your head!

1043
01:48:42,391 --> 01:48:44,475
Don't look at me.

1044
01:48:47,145 --> 01:48:50,314
Don't look at me, please.

1045
01:48:52,150 --> 01:48:55,903
- Don't look at me!
- Put the knife down!

1046
01:48:58,657 --> 01:49:00,449
Put it down!

1047
01:49:01,159 --> 01:49:04,662
What are you doing?
Put the knife down!

1048
01:49:46,121 --> 01:49:48,372
I will go blind, won't I?

1049
01:49:53,629 --> 01:49:55,713
How long do I have?

1050
01:49:57,674 --> 01:50:00,009
You'll go blind before dawn.

1051
01:50:08,602 --> 01:50:11,103
I need you to do me a favor.

1052
01:50:43,428 --> 01:50:45,262
Can we have a moment?

1053
01:50:55,107 --> 01:50:56,649
What happened to his eyes?

1054
01:50:59,194 --> 01:51:01,278
He donated them.

1055
01:51:07,786 --> 01:51:09,328
And where are they?

1056
01:51:10,080 --> 01:51:12,373
Where he would have wanted.

1057
01:51:20,966 --> 01:51:23,509
Isaac, why?

1058
01:51:25,345 --> 01:51:28,639
My God, I miss you so much.

1059
01:51:33,562 --> 01:51:36,147
You promised me.

1060
01:51:36,314 --> 01:51:39,442
You promised me.

1061
01:52:22,611 --> 01:52:26,197
You told me
that when you looked into my eyes...

1062
01:52:27,032 --> 01:52:29,158
...you could see the entire universe.

1063
01:52:30,202 --> 01:52:32,203
I still can.

1064
01:53:28,134 --> 01:53:31,804
JULIA'S EYES

